{"tid":290773,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"任天堂Switch推3.0版本Firmware更新","createTime":"2017-06-20T04:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T06:32:50.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"497fc5b09f93fb0821e7634a5593b22f94b9ce70","tid":290773,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T04:47:40.000Z","msg":"雖然任天堂嘅Switch正式推出都唔係好耐，但已經推出過幾次小型嘅Firmware更新，而之前主要都係提升系統嘅穩定性。但今次推出全新嘅3.0版本，就令你手上部Switch新增更多功能，大家都係拿拿林拎部機出嚟Update啦！<br />\n喺正常情況下只要將Switch連上互聯網，就會自動更新。但用家仍然可以選擇手動更新，只係即使選擇手動更新，Switch仍然係需要連到上互聯網先。<br />\n<br />\n以下係3.0版本Firmware更新/新增功能：<br />\n1, 可以註冊新聞頻道以接收指定遊戲嘅新聞。<br />\n2, 喺原本3DS同Wii U嘅Friend Lists入面搵返啲Friend嚟加返。<br />\n3, 當朋友Online時會收到通知（可選擇開關）。<br />\n4, 可以遙控震動手機等你搵返佢（要喺收入節圍內）。<br />\n5, 可轉換用家圖示嘅次序。<br />\n6, 多咗6個新圖示畀用家選用。<br />\n7, 可以喺Quick Settings入面調校音量。<br />\n8, 可限制Audio Jack嘅最高輸出量。<br />\n9, 可將系統介面色彩倒轉或者設定灰階。<br />\n10, 可以以USB線連接Switch Pro Controller變成有線連接。<br />\n11, 可以更新控制器。<br />\n12, 當系統容量不足時會自動建議可刪除嘅資料。<br />\n13, 解決遊戲更新失敗會令遊戲不能啟動嘅問題。<br />\n14, 改善部份電視機於Switch以HDMI連接並進入休息模式時會自動轉去其他輸入嘅問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkgolden.com/articles/article.aspx?id=24959&amp;catid=35\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgolden.com%2Farticles%2Farticle.aspx%3Fid%3D24959%26catid%3D35&d=lURBPqGZ1zWsXjaBHnjKH7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=28cb1b11\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkgolden.com/articles/article.aspx?id=24959&amp;catid=35</a>"},{"pid":"606bf16b0e0a9ee4864753c3c7425cf3e8dbfc13","tid":290773,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:10:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b14da60d5a086b4f71ceee0dffd5c08be1add7","tid":290773,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T06:14:22.000Z","msg":"近排你出老任post咁客觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比個正評你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7992e4adb87c778a65ed1c05cbb279c407f20ab8","tid":290773,"uid":35408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T06:15:58.000Z","msg":"有冇人放機<br />\n想收  要行 有保養<br />\n留tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92aa9fc1052de84cf2bfacb61573d362d45d7038","tid":290773,"uid":14054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T06:17:50.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾幾時有得backup save<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b359af90b2dff4cfd78f5cfef3db3ed3a9ab454","tid":290773,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T06:32:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃撚圾幾時有得backup save<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能要等4.0或5.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}